name: Get Durty! Live EP (UK ORDERS ONLY)
description:
(THIS CD CAN ONLY BE POSTED TO UK RESIDENTS) (orders can also not be sent to ireland) Kraken’s Debut EP Recorded Live at the cellar bar in bracknell features 5 tracks + one bonus acoustic track for store purchases only!

Track Listing 1. Lost My Grip 2. The Kraken Show 3. Paying Your Death Installments 4. Transient Insomnia 5. Forever Lost 6. Quite! We’ll Wake The Neighbours
